name: WindChimes
skdetail:

Invocation Name: wind chimes
des:
Play some relaxing wind chime sounds.

Listen to Wind Chimes by adding to a Daily Routine. To add this skill to a daily timer, follow these steps:

On Alexa app, navigate to Routines.
Click + to add a new routine.
Click + for "When this happens" and choose one.
Click + for "Add action" and choose "Skills".
Choose "Your Skills" > Select Wind Chimes
Choose Device to perform the routine > SAVE.

If you enjoyed this skill, please leave a review.
